{{italic title}} '''''Berlin''''' is a 2009 play by [[David Hare (playwright)|David Hare]], in the form of a 55-minute monologue on [[Berlin]] and its [[history of Berlin|history]]. It was first performed in March 2009 at the [[Royal National Theatre]] by the author himself, directed by [[Stephen Daldry]].
